{"tid":2233406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台或禁大學私訂「一中承諾」","createTime":"2020-10-07T06:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:36:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3d2803c4f3885bb1e930aeda388c4244daf587","tid":2233406,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201007/DD7U2PVE3BFGDNA4LNQDYDAATY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201007%2FDD7U2PVE3BFGDNA4LNQDYDAATY%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=37e5e447\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201007%2FDD7U2PVE3BFGDNA4LNQDYDAATY%2F&h=a7ca5fad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201007/DD7U2PVE3BFGDNA4LNQDYDAATY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台或禁大學私訂「一中承諾」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ETsQ-lqrmmL77ACrfE3Qc2RdieI=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/62YBBYDAVJCQDJ2UWEAJVXAOBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FETsQ-lqrmmL77ACrfE3Qc2RdieI%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F62YBBYDAVJCQDJ2UWEAJVXAOBQ.jpg&h=c8584d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘇貞昌形容國民黨提出「台美復交」是良心發現。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，台灣的大學近年為招收大陸留學生及研修生，有接近四成半、即72家大學應大陸要求私下簽署「一中承諾書」等政治聲明，但至今仍然沒有任何相應罰則，行政院長蘇貞昌昨表示，學術交流不該有政治條款。有台灣立法委員也提案修法，要求禁大學私訂「一中承諾書」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蘇貞昌：國民黨良心發現 「台美復交」提案 藍綠無異議通過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘇貞昌促教育部盤查<br />\n<br />\n台灣《自由時報》報道，自2017年台灣世新大學為開放大陸學生前往台灣交流，與江蘇師範大學等大陸的大學簽訂研修承諾書，承諾課程內容絕不涉及政治敏感活動，不得從事任何「一中一台」、「兩個中國」、「台灣獨立」等活動，引來輿論譁然。台灣教育部當年3月公佈調查結果，稱台灣的157家大專，有72家曾簽署類似的「一中承諾書」，但至今未有任何一家大學遭罰。<br />\n<br />\n蘇貞昌（圖）昨往立法院報告「中央政府前瞻基礎建設計劃第三期特別預算案」，。。。。。。。。。相關補助或禁止其招生。<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》"},{"pid":"a27cc3bb101c908eb8a26d87aff2d9fce2a8c2e3","tid":2233406,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66d8c1a2d904395f648e26d1477868c48655becf","tid":2233406,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"做得好，小心共匪滲透 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43956c03dd6c6cadb6fd51e2832c0e247967f3a8","tid":2233406,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"屌！點解人地個政府咁撚做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}